[OWNER] — confirmed decisions only. An entry goes here **only** when the owner has
explicitly accepted it. The agent proposes; the owner confirms; then it's logged.

# decisions_log.md — what I've decided

> This is the agent's memory of your settled choices, so it never re-litigates them.
> Newest at the top.
>
> 확정한 선택의 기록. 에이전트가 이미 끝난 결정을 다시 꺼내지 않도록. 최신이 위.

Entry format:
```
### YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM · [what was decided]
Source: [conversation / meeting / direct statement]
Decision: [the confirmed choice]
Tags: [확정 confirmed] / [메모 note] / [충돌 conflict]
```

If a new decision conflicts with an old one, mark `[충돌]` and cross-reference — don't
silently overwrite. The owner resolves conflicts, not the agent.

